title: The Twilight Zone - The Last Rites Of Jeff Myrtlebank
description: Everyone at Jeff Myrtlebank's funeral service is shocked when he pushes the coffin lid open and steps out, seemingly in perfect health. Old Doc Bolton mumbles some ridiculous explanation and the people there settle down a bit.
